burn off energy productively.\\\\n\\\\nThe layout at North Elizabeth Dog Grooming is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\\\",\\\"slug\\\":\\\"north-elizabeth-dog-grooming\\\",\\\"address\\\":\\\"704 Jackson Ave\\\",\\\"street\\\":\\\"704 Jackson Ave\\\",\\\"city\\\":\\\"Elizabeth\\\",\\\"state\\\":\\\"NJ\\\",\\\"zipCode\\\":\\\"07201\\\",\\\"full_address\\\":\\\"704 Jackson Ave, Elizabeth, NJ 07201, USA\\\",\\\"latitude\\\":40.67665530000001,\\\"longitude\\\":-74.2011322,\\\"googlePlaceId\\\":\\\"ChIJWz0Za1NTwokRXyV2Q8Ef19w\\\",\\\"phone\\\":\\\"(908) 327-8504\\\",\\\"website\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"photos\\\":null,\\\"rating\\\":5,\\\"reviewCount\\\":32,\\\"openingHours\\\":{\\\"Monday\\\":\\\"8:00 AM – 6:00 PM\\\",\\\"Tuesday\\\":\\\"Closed\\\",\\\"Wednesday\\\":\\\"8:00 AM – 6:00 PM\\\",\\\"Thursday\\\":\\\"8:00 AM – 6:00 PM\\\",\\\"Friday\\\":\\\"8:00 AM – 6:00 PM\\\",\\\"Saturday\\\":\\\"8:00 AM – 6:00 PM\\\",\\\"Sunday\\\":\\\"9:00 AM – 5:00 PM\\\"},\\\"amenities\\\":{\\\"Onsite services\\\":true,\\\"Indoor facilities\\\":true,\\\"Professional staff\\\":true,\\\"Climate controlled\\\":true,\\\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\\\":false,\\\"Parking available\\\":true,\\\"Easy access\\\":true},\\\"pricing\\\":{\\\"pricingSource\\\":\\\"website\\\",\\\"isFree\\\":false},\\\"placeTypes\\\":[\\\"point_of_interest\\\",\\\"establishment\\\"],\\\"lastUpdated\\\":null,\\\"dataQuality\\\":\\\"verified\\\",\\\"photo\\\":null,\\\"faqs\\\":[],\\\"source\\\":\\\"static\\\",\\\"listingType\\\":\\\"free\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"ChIJR0tDLSdNwokRaGeVQse1vUM\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Pawrty Time - Dog Training\\\",\\\"businessType\\\":\\\"Dog Park\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Serious about your pup's fitness and focus? Pawrty Time - Dog Training in [Elizabeth](/cities/elizabeth-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.5 stars by a community of 15 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of \\\\\\\"constructive play.\\\\\\\" It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\\\\n\\\\nThe layout at Pawrty Time - Dog Training is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\\\",\\\"slug\\\":\\\"pawrty-time-dog-training\\\",\\\"address\\\":\\\"310 Pine St\\\",\\\"street\\\":\\\"310 Pine St\\\",\\\"city\\\":\\\"Elizabeth\\\",\\\"state\\\":\\\"NJ\\\",\\\"zipCode\\\":\\\"07206\\\",\\\"full_address\\\":\\\"310 Pine St, Elizabeth, NJ 07206, USA\\\",\\\"latitude\\\":40.655144,\\\"longitude\\\":-74.18652000000002,\\\"googlePlaceId\\\":\\\"ChIJR0tDLSdNwokRaGeVQse1vUM\\\",\\\"phone\\\":\\\"(929) 417-1111\\\",\\\"website\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"photos\\\":null,\\\"rating\\\":0,\\\"reviewCount\\\":0,\\\"openingHours\\\":{\\\"Monday\\\":\\\"9:30 AM – 7:30 PM\\\",\\\"Tuesday\\\":\\\"9:30 AM – 7:30 PM\\\",\\\"Wednesday\\\":\\\"9:30 AM – 7:30 PM\\\",\\\"Thursday\\\":\\\"9:30 AM – 7:30 PM\\\",\\\"Friday\\\":\\\"9:30 AM – 7:30 PM\\\",\\\"Saturday\\\":\\\"10:00 AM – 7:30 PM\\\",\\\"Sunday\\\":\\\"2:00 – 8:30 PM\\\"},\\\"amenities\\\":{\\\"Onsite services\\\":true,\\\"Indoor facilities\\\":true,\\\"Professional staff\\\":true,\\\"Climate controlled\\\":true,\\\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\\\":false,\\\"Parking available\\\":true,\\\"Easy access\\\":true},\\\"pricing\\\":{\\\"pricingSource\\\":\\\"website\\\",\\\"isFree\\\":false},\\\"placeTypes\\\":[\\\"point_of_interest\\\",\\\"establishment\\\"],\\\"lastUpdated\\\":null,\\\"dataQuality\\\":\\\"verified\\\",\\\"photo\\\":null,\\\"faqs\\\":[],\\\"source\\\":\\\"static\\\",\\\"listingType\\\":\\\"free\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"ChIJ8VhYOletw4kRVkF9oP5tWfg\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Phil Rizzuto Park\\\",\\\"businessType\\\":\\\"Dog Park\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Serious about your pup's fitness and focus? Phil Rizzuto Park in [North Ave](/cities/north-ave-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.5 stars by a community of 838 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of \\\\\\\"constructive play.\\\\\\\" It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\\\\n\\\\nThe layout at Phil Rizzuto Park is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\\\",\\\"slug\\\":\\\"phil-rizzuto-park\\\",\\\"address\\\":\\\"\\u0026\\\",\\\"street\\\":\\\"\\u0026\\\",\\\"city\\\":\\\"Elizabeth\\\",\\\"state\\\":\\\"NJ\\\",\\\"zipCode\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"full_address\\\":\\\"\\u0026, North Ave, Elizabeth, NJ 07208, USA\\\",\\\"latitude\\\":40.67533859999999,\\\"longitude\\\":-74.2272206,\\\"googlePlaceId\\\":\\\"ChIJ8VhYOletw4kRVkF9oP5tWfg\\\",\\\"phone\\\":\\\"(908) 527-4900\\\",\\\"website\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"photos\\\":null,\\\"rating\\\":4.5,\\\"reviewCount\\\":838,\\\"openingHours\\\":{\\\"Monday\\\":\\\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\\\",\\\"Tuesday\\\":\\\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\\\",\\\"Wednesday\\\":\\\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\\\",\\\"Thursday\\\":\\\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\\\",\\\"Friday\\\":\\\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\\\",\\\"Saturday\\\":\\\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\\\",\\\"Sunday\\\":\\\"5:00 AM – 8:00 PM\\\"},\\\"amenities\\\":{\\\"Onsite services\\\":true,\\\"Indoor facilities\\\":true,\\\"Professional staff\\\":true,\\\"Climate controlled\\\":true,\\\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\\\":true,\\\"Parking available\\\":true,\\\"Easy access\\\":true},\\\"pricing\\\":{\\\"pricingSource\\\":\\\"website\\\",\\\"isFree\\\":false},\\\"placeTypes\\\":[\\\"point_of_interest\\\",\\\"establishment\\\"],\\\"lastUpdated\\\":null,\\\"dataQuality\\\":\\\"verified\\\",\\\"photo\\\":null,\\\"faqs\\\":[],\\\"source\\\":\\\"static\\\",\\\"listingType\\\":\\\"free\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"ChIJfyM6NLuyw4kRImxLqMZfWeE\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Poodle Splash\\\",\\\"businessType\\\":\\\"Dog Park\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"If you're looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Elizabeth](/cities/elizabeth-nj), look no further than Poodle Splash. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the \\\\\\\"place to be\\\\\\\" for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 4.5-star rating from 23 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop wagging and neighbors become friends. Whether you're there for a quick playdate or a long afternoon of socializing, the atmosphere is always buzzing with positivity.\\\\n\\\\nAt Poodle Splash, the focus is on connection. The layout encourages interaction, making it easy for pups to find playmates while owners chat on the sidelines. It’s not just a facility; it’s a social pillar of the Elizabeth scene, offering a safe, clean, and joyous environment where every visitor feels like a VIP. For a fun, friendly, and community-centered experience, this spot is a local favorite.\\\",\\\"slug\\\":\\\"poodle-splash\\\",\\\"