 safe. It is more than just a plot of land; it is a repository of memories for families and a daily ritual for the neighborhood. For those who value consistency, heritage, and a strong sense of place, this Elizabeth staple remains the gold standard.\",\"slug\":\"rest-inn-elizabeth\",\"address\":\"454 Maple Ave\",\"street\":\"454 Maple Ave\",\"city\":\"Elizabeth\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07202\",\"full_address\":\"454 Maple Ave, Elizabeth, NJ 07202, USA\",\"latitude\":40.6533007,\"longitude\":-74.21356449999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJvxfUkktNwokRMmYU5JGicpY\",\"phone\":\"(908) 469-7277\",\"website\":\"\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":2.5,\"reviewCount\":100,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Tuesday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Wednesday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Thursday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Friday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Saturday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Sunday\":\"Open 24 hours\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJ9zVVSFVNwokRt3YEpfN72Ic\",\"name\":\"Rex Grooming\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"For years, Rex Grooming has served as a steadfast anchor of the [Elizabeth](/cities/elizabeth-nj) community, earning its place as a beloved local institution. With a history of serving generations of tail-waggers, this location carries a sense of established trust and neighborhood pride that you can't manufacture. Documented by 23 reviews and a 4.2-star legacy, it stands as a testament to the town's enduring commitment to its animal residents.\\n\\nStepping into Rex Grooming feels like visiting an old friend. The facility balances traditional park values with modern maintenance standards, ensuring a timeless experience that feels both familiar and safe. It is more than just a plot of land; it is a repository of memories for families and a daily ritual for the neighborhood. For those who value consistency, heritage, and a strong sense of place, this Elizabeth staple remains the gold standard.\",\"slug\":\"rex-grooming\",\"address\":\"251 Union St\",\"street\":\"251 Union St\",\"city\":\"Elizabeth\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07208\",\"full_address\":\"251 Union St, Elizabeth, NJ 07208, USA\",\"latitude\":40.6683279,\"longitude\":-74.2173811,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJ9zVVSFVNwokRt3YEpfN72Ic\",\"phone\":\"(908) 943-3684\",\"website\":\"\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.2,\"reviewCount\":23,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"9:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"9:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"9:00 AM – 5:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"9:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"9:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"9:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"9:00 AM – 6:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJ3awUH0tNwokRMfmZCySgQQw\",\"name\":\"Ritz Motel\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"If you're looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Elizabeth](/cities/elizabeth-nj), look no further than Ritz Motel. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the \\\"place to be\\\" for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 3.3-star rating from 277 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop