ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}]\n32:[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]\n33:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Data refreshed weekly\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Data refreshed weekly\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Live availability coming soon\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Live availability coming soon\"]}]]}]\n34:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L43\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/cities/elizabeth/hero.webp\",\"alt\":\"Elizabeth dog park landscape\",\"fill\":true,\"priority\":true,\"sizes\":\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 540px\",\"unoptimized\":true}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-gradient\"}]]}]}]\n35:[\"$\",\"$L44\",null,{\"city\":\"Elizabeth\",\"state\":\"NJ\"}]\n46:T43d,For years, Carteret Park has served as a steadfast anchor of the [NJ 07202](/cities/nj-07202-nj) community, earning its place as a beloved local institution. With a history of serving generations of tail-waggers, this location carries a sense of established trust and neighborhood pride that you can't manufacture. Documented by 308 reviews and a 4.5-star legacy, it stands as a testament to the town's enduring commitment to its animal residents.\n\nStepping into Carteret Park feels like visiting an old friend. The facility balances traditional park values with modern maintenance standards, ensuring a timeless experience that feels both familiar and safe. It is more than just a plot of land; it is a repository of memories for families and a daily ritual for the neighborhood. For those who value consistency, heritage, and a strong sense of place, this NJ 07202 staple remains the gold standard.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://www.elizabethnj.org/Facilities/Facility/Details/Carteret-Park-13) to learn more about their services and updated hours.47:T422,Serious about your pup's fitness and focus? City Paws Pet Grooming in [Elizabeth](/cities/elizabeth-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.3 stars by a community of 287 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of \"constructive play.\" It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\n\nThe layout at City Paws Pet Grooming is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](http://www.citypawselizabeth.com/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.48:T474,If you're looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Elizabeth](/cities/elizabeth-nj), look no further than Elizabeth Country Kennels. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the \"place to be\" for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 4.9-star rating from 38 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop wagging and neighbors become friends. Whether you're there for a quick playdate or a long afternoon of socializing, the atmosphere is always buzzing with positivity.\n\nAt Elizabeth Country Kennels, the focus is on connection. The layout encourages interaction, making it easy for pups to find playmates while owners chat on the sidelines. It’s not just a facility; it’s a social pillar of the Elizabeth scene, offering a safe, clean, and joyous environment where every visitor feels like a VIP. For a fun, friendly, and community-centered experience, this spot is a local favorite.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](http://elizabethcountrykennels.com/) to learn more about their services and updated hours.49:T48d,If you're looking for the ultimate wag-worthy social hub in [Elizabeth](/cities/elizabeth-nj), look no further than Elizabeth Pet Grooming. This vibrant community destination has earned a reputation as the \"place to be\" for local pet parents who want more than just a walk—they want a meetup. Boasting a solid 4.7-star rating from 327 reviews, the park radiates a welcoming energy where tails never stop wagging and neighbors become friends. Whether you're there for a quick playdate or a long afternoon of socializing, the atmosphere is always buzzing with positivity.\n\nAt Elizabeth Pet Grooming, the focus is on connection. The layout encourages interaction, making it easy for pups to find playmates while owners chat on the sidelines. It’s not just a facility; it’s a social pillar of the Elizabeth scene, offering a safe, clean, and joyous environment where every visitor feels like a VIP. For a fun, friendly, and community-centered experience, this spot is a local favorite.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://www.petgroomerfinder.com/salon/elizabeth-pet-grooming-llc) to learn more about their services and updated hours.4a:T4dd,Serious about your pup's fitness and focus? Extended Stay America Suites - Elizabeth - Newark Airport in [Elizabeth](/cities/elizabeth-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 3.4 stars by a community of 1224 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of \"construc