Rest Inn - Elizabeth\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"For years, Rest Inn - Elizabeth has served as a steadfast anchor of the [Elizabeth](/cities/elizabeth-nj) community, earning its place as a beloved local institution. With a history of serving generations of tail-waggers, this location carries a sense of established trust and neighborhood pride that you can't manufacture. Documented by 100 reviews and a 2.5-star legacy, it stands as a testament to the town's enduring commitment to its animal residents.\\n\\nStepping into Rest Inn - Elizabeth feels like visiting an old friend. The facility balances traditional park values with modern maintenance standards, ensuring a timeless experience that feels both familiar and safe. It is more than just a plot of land; it is a repository of memories for families and a daily ritual for the neighborhood. For those who value consistency, heritage, and a strong sense of place, this Elizabeth staple remains the gold standard.\",\"slug\":\"rest-inn-elizabeth\",\"address\":\"454 Maple Ave\",\"street\":\"454 Maple Ave\",\"city\":\"Elizabeth\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07202\",\"full_address\":\"454 Maple Ave, Elizabeth, NJ 07202, USA\",\"latitude\":40.6533007,\"longitude\":-74.21356449999999,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJvxfUkktNwokRMmYU5JGicpY\",\"phone\":\"(908) 469-7277\",\"website\":\"\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":2.5,\"reviewCount\":100,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Tuesday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Wednesday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Thursday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Friday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Saturday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Sunday\":\"Open 24 hours\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"data